      "text": "[image blog/pesos-vs-posse resize=false] Here is the potential impact of each approach: <table> <thead> <tr> <th> </th> <th>PESOS</th> <th>POSSE</th> </tr> </thead> <tr> <td> <em>Dependence</em> </td> <td>A 3rd party is a required intermediary within the PESOS approach.",
